OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774537863
OL,3,CNuclear power plant comes under
OL,4,C'enhanced regulatory attention'
OL,5,Cfollowing checks
OL,7,FA nuclear power plant in Hartlepool
OL,8,Fhas been placed into the
OL,9,F"significantly-enhanced regulatory
OL,10,Fattention" category, the Office for
OL,11,FNuclear Regulation (ONR) has said.
OL,13,FThe decision was made after visits to
OL,14,Fthe site, operated by EDF, identified
OL,15,Fareas where safety improvements were
OL,16,Frequired.
OL,18,FThe ONR said the nuclear power plant
OL,19,Fremained safe to continue to operate.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
