CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774537863
OL,3,CNuclear power plant comes under
OL,4,C'enhanced regulatory attention'
OL,5,Cfollowing checks
OL,7,FIt said the "significantly-enhanced
OL,8,Fregulatory attention level" related to
OL,9,Fefforts the ONR was making to bring
OL,10,Fabout improvements in conventional
OL,11,Fhealth and safety and performance.
OL,13,FDan Hasted, ONR's director of
OL,14,Fregulation for operating facilities,
OL,15,Fsaid: "When required, we place sites
OL,16,Finto significantly-enhanced attention
OL,17,Fto achieve improved performance in
OL,18,Fspecific areas.
OL,20,F"This is a key part of our role as an
OL,21,Findependent regulator.
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@[O]wD@GOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
