PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774537863
OL,3,CNuclear power plant comes under
OL,4,C'enhanced regulatory attention'
OL,5,Cfollowing checks
OL,7,F"EDF is committed to delivering a
OL,8,Frange of improvements at Hartlepool,
OL,9,Fand we are overseeing this. Through
OL,10,Four enabling regulatory approach, we
OL,11,Fare working constructively with the
OL,12,Flicensee to ensure all these issues
OL,13,Fare addressed."
OL,15,FThe Hartlepool site operates two gas-
OL,16,Fcooled reactors and it has generated
OL,17,Felectricity for the past 43 years.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
