OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774537863
OL,3,CNuclear power plant comes under
OL,4,C'enhanced regulatory attention'
OL,5,Cfollowing checks
OL,7,FEDF said it was committed to making
OL,8,Fimprovements and said the regulator
OL,9,Fwill visit the site more regularly,
OL,10,Fcarrying out additional inspections.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the firm said:
OL,13,F"Hartlepool power station has been a
OL,14,Fvital part of the Teesside community
OL,15,Ffor more than 40 years and it is
OL,16,Fimportant to note the ONR has been
OL,17,Fclear that the site continues to be
OL,18,Fsafe to operate.
OL,20,F"Last year we agreed an improvement
OL,21,Fplan with the regulator.
OL,26,@uD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774537863
OL,3,CNuclear power plant comes under
OL,4,C'enhanced regulatory attention'
OL,5,Cfollowing checks
OL,7,F"We have been making progress against
OL,8,Fthat plan but understand the ONR feels
OL,9,Fthat some more focused attention is
OL,10,Frequired to support that.
OL,12,F"What this change means is that the
OL,13,Fregulator will visit the site more
OL,14,Fregularly and carry out additional
OL,15,Finspections.
OL,17,F"We are committed to working with the
OL,18,Fregulator to ensure it is content that
OL,19,Fimprovements required are being
OL,20,Fimplemented."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
